            "icon": "box",
            "row_content": "<p>At <strong>Indivibe<\/strong>, we offer a wide range of products, including <strong>kids' toys 🧸<\/strong>, <strong>gym equipment 🏋️<\/strong>, <strong>personal care items 🛀<\/strong>, <strong>kitchen tools 🍳<\/strong>, and more!<\/p>",
