          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. How can I place an order?",
            "icon": "eye",
            "row_content": "<p>Placing an order is easy! Browse our products, add your favorites to the cart 🛒, and proceed to checkout. You’ll receive a confirmation email once your order is placed.<\/p><h4><\/h4>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
